    question: "Which is a disorder dominated by prominent psychomotor disturbances that may alternate between extremes such as hyperkinesis and stupor, or automatic obedience and negativism? Choose 1 item.",
    options: ["Delusional disorder", "Schizotypal disorder", "Paranoid schizophrenia", "Catatonic schizophrenia", "Hebephrenic schizophrenia"],
